  "remarks": "CDi.012 Designation: a) FDLR-FOCA Commander b) FDLR-FOCA Lieutenant General.  The International Criminal Court issued an arrest warrant for Mudacumura on 12 July 2012 for nine counts of war crimes, including attacking civilians, murder, mutilation, cruel treatment, rape, torture, destruction of property, pillaging and outrages against personal dignity, allegedly committed between 2009 and 2010 in the DRC.; Listing: Listed by 1533 Committee on: 1 Nov. 2005 (amended on 13 Oct. 2016)",
